<li><i>Dawn &amp; Decline</i></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Dialectic_of_Enlightenment" title="Dialectic of Enlightenment">Dialectic of Enlightenment</a></i> (1947) - with <a href="/wiki/Theodor_Adorno" title="Theodor Adorno" class="mw-redirect">Theodor Adorno</a></li>
